{"tid":1802403,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］屋企人電話號碼被盜用 求救","createTime":"2019-12-29T12:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T03:01:07.000Z","uid":142019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1dbb85db345d43329bb62fd767eae72b2a5fd0","tid":1802403,"uid":142019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"一朝早勁多強國電話號碼打電話過黎 ，間唔中有香港既 。個個都話我屋企人個號碼打比佢先，跟住人地打番轉頭 ，一係就同人講佢係咩京東購物⋯。<br />\n重有個大陸佬 半個鐘 打左40幾次電話黎，我較左免打擾，佢留口訊屌我屋企人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去hkbn門市問，佢叫我打上客服。我打去客服，客服又話睇過狀態冇異常，一係報警 一係轉號碼。我地話諗諗先。cut左線先發現 依家咁既環境其實都唔洗諗⋯<br />\n<br />\n我地又打番去客服，佢又話要屋企電話先比轉，手機唔得要得完約 ，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係冇辦法 誠求各位巴打集思廣益幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬冇咩j圖比大家做報酬 就比個大陸個痴線佬電話笑下<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvLH82S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvLH82S.jpg&h=dbb48063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dba2517c6558a5d1a32a74ae8974245de84451e","tid":1802403,"uid":142019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家幫幫手"},{"pid":"5892bb672a00a1a26a3846e278d51c1b43a1661b","tid":1802403,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"裝apps block咗呢類電話?"},{"pid":"20de090ad1882e32ffdada3bc46026388741261c","tid":1802403,"uid":142019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"都好多 成日睇youtube會閃一下 同埋呢類唔算推廣電話 要一次封晒冇save電話既都打唔入"},{"pid":"e58df4f5fc5eaf0b6a90770a62c4e1b7f01c94dd","tid":1802403,"uid":3008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"試下打過過嚟嘅number都block咗先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b17ccd907e17142ce982737a197006c460413f","tid":1802403,"uid":142019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20